                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.48/1865.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul <persName type="from">Garrett</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Nuevo Laredo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-09-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 28, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>A few American refugees have been coming from Mexico and applying for
                    transportation during August and September. I sent out six persons from Tampico
                    district Saturday. Is there fund still available for transportation destitute
                    refugees?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Garrett</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
